This is an action RPG boss battle. Avoid the enemy's attacks

Arousal can be dispelled by walking around a certain number
of steps. It can also be dispelled by shaking off a critical

Learn the enemy's attack patterns. The enemy's attacks have
patterns. First, focus on avoiding them to learn.

Make use of the D key's direction lock. Locking your
direction makes it easier to attack and evade. Attacking
while backing away can make the fight easier.

Use healing items and skills. There are no usage
restrictions on healing items and skills (such as deep
breathing). It is possible to heal and push through
aggressively.

Use the Action Easer option. By turning on the Action Easer
from the options, the difficulty level will significantly
decrease. There are no disadvantages.
